#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Optional _metadata_ -- arbitrary key-value pairs attached to the emission."
msgstr "可选 _元数据_ ——附加到发射事件上的 _任意_ 键值对。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The combination of signal type and qualifiers determines which receivers are notified when a signal is emitted."
msgstr "信号类型与限定条件的组合决定了在发出信号时，哪些接收器会收到通知。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, suppose we have a signal object of type `OrderPlaced`:"
msgstr "例如，假设我们有一个类型为 `OrderPlaced` 的信号对象："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Signal objects should be immutable or thread-safe, because they can be accessed from multiple threads concurrently."
msgstr "信号对象应为不可变的或线程安全的，因为多个线程可能会同时访问它们。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We could define a qualifier to distinguish urgent orders:"
msgstr "我们可以定义一个限定符来区分紧急订单："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Emitting Signals"
msgstr "发出信号"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `Signal` interface is the entry point for emitting signals.\n"
"An application component obtains a `Signal` instance by injecting it as a CDI bean:"
msgstr "`Signal` 接口是发出信号的入口点。应用程序组件通过将其作为 CDI Bean 注入来获取 `Signal` 实例："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Any combination of qualifiers may be specified at the injection point:"
msgstr "在注入点处可以指定任意组合的限定条件："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When CDI injection is not available (e.g. in a static method or a class that is not a CDI bean), a `Signal` instance can be created programmatically using the `Signal.create()` factory method:"
msgstr "当无法使用 CDI 注入时（例如在静态方法中，或在一个非 CDI Bean 的类中），可以通过 `Signal.create()` 工厂方法以编程方式创建 `Signal` 实例："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For parameterized signal types, use `TypeLiteral`:"
msgstr "对于参数化信号类型，请使用 `TypeLiteral` ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A signal can be emitted in three modes."
msgstr "信号可以通过三种模式发出。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Publish (Multicast)"
msgstr "发布（多播）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Delivers the signal to _all_ matching receivers."
msgstr "将信号传输至 _所有_ 匹配的接收器。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Send (Unicast)"
msgstr "发送（单播）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Delivers the signal to a _single_ matching receiver, selected in round-robin order."
msgstr "将信号传输至 _一个_ 匹配的接收器，该接收器按轮询顺序选定。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Request (Unicast, Request-Reply)"
msgstr "请求（单播，请求-响应）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delivers the signal to a _single_ matching receiver and returns the response.\n"
"Only receivers whose response type is assignable to the requested type are considered."
msgstr "将信号发送给 _一个_ 匹配的接收器，并返回响应。仅考虑响应类型可分配给请求类型的接收器。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Selecting Subtypes and Qualifiers"
msgstr "选择子类型和限定词"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A child `Signal` can be obtained from an existing one in order to narrow the type or add qualifiers:"
msgstr "可以从现有的 `Signal` 派生出一个子 `Signal` ，以便缩小类型范围或添加限定条件："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Signal Metadata"
msgstr "信号元数据"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Arbitrary key-value metadata can be attached to an emission.\n"
"Receivers can access this metadata via the `SignalContext`."
msgstr "可以在发射事件中附加任意的键值元数据。接收方可以通过 `SignalContext` 访问这些元数据。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Both `withMetadata()` and `withReplacedMetadata()` return a new child `Signal` instance; the original instance is not modified."
msgstr "`withMetadata()` 和 `withReplacedMetadata()` 都会返回一个新的子 `Signal` 实例；原始实例不会被修改。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "No Matching Receiver"
msgstr "未找到匹配的接收器"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If no receiver matches the emitted signal:"
msgstr "如果没有接收器与发出的信号匹配："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`publish()` and `send()` succeed silently -- no error is raised."
msgstr "`publish()` 和 `send()` 执行成功时不会输出任何信息——不会抛出错误。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`request()` returns `null`."
msgstr "`request()` 返回 `null` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`reactive().publish()`, `reactive().send()` and `reactive().request()` complete with a `null` item."
msgstr "`reactive().publish()` 、 `reactive().send()` 和 `reactive().request()` 返回一个 `null` 项。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Lazy Uni Semantics"
msgstr "懒惰的Uni语义学"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `Uni` returned by `reactive().publish()`, `reactive().send()`, and `reactive().request()` is _lazy_: no signal is emitted until the `Uni` is subscribed.\n"
"Each subscription triggers a new, independent emission."
msgstr "通过 `reactive().publish()` 、 `reactive().send()` 和 `reactive().request()` 返回的 `Uni` 是 _懒加载的_ ：在有人订阅该 `Uni` 之前，不会发出任何信号。每次订阅都会触发一次新的、独立的信号发布。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Error Handling"
msgstr "错误处理"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For blocking emission methods (`publish()`, `send()`, and `request()`), receiver failures from `publish()` and `send()` are logged but not propagated to the caller.\n"
"For `request()`, the receiver's exception is thrown directly on the calling thread; a checked exception is wrapped in a `java.util.concurrent.CompletionException`."
msgstr "对于阻塞式发布方法（ `publish()` 、 `send()` 和 `request()` ），来自 `publish()` 和 `send()` 的接收方故障会被记录，但不会传播给调用方。对于 `request()` ，接收方的异常会直接在调用线程上抛出；受检查的异常会被封装在 `java.util.concurrent.CompletionException` 中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For reactive emission methods (`reactive().publish()`, `reactive().send()`, and `reactive().request()`), the failure is propagated through the returned `Uni`.\n"
"For `send` and `request` emissions (unicast), the receiver's exception is propagated directly.\n"
"For `publish` emissions (multicast), where multiple receivers may fail, the failures are wrapped in a `io.smallrye.mutiny.CompositeException`."
msgstr "对于响应式发射方法（ `reactive().publish()` 、 `reactive().send()` 和 `reactive().request()` ），故障会通过返回的 `Uni` 进行传播。对于 `send` 和 `request` 发射（单播），接收方的异常会直接传播。 对于 `发布型` 发射（多播），由于可能存在多个接收方发生故障，这些故障会被封装在 `io.smallrye.mutiny.CompositeException` 中。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Receiver Methods"
msgstr "接收器方法"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A _receiver method_ is a non-private, non-static method declared on a CDI bean.\n"
"It must have exactly one parameter annotated with `@Receives`.\n"
"The type of the annotated parameter determines the _received signal type_.\n"
"Additional parameters may be declared and are treated as injection points -- the container will obtain and inject the corresponding bean instances when the receiver is invoked, just like https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1#observes[CDI observer methods]."
msgstr "_接收器方法_ 是在 CDI Bean 上声明的、非私有且非静态的方法。它必须恰好有一个标注了 `@Receives` 注解的参数。 该注解参数的类型决定了 _接收信号_ 的 _类型_ 。可以声明其他参数，这些参数将被视为注入点——当接收器被调用时，容器会获取并注入相应的 Bean 实例，这与 link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1#observes[CDI 观察者方法的处理方式] 相同。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Qualifiers"
msgstr "资格赛"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Qualifiers declared on the annotated parameter are used during type-safe resolution.\n"
"If a receiver declares no qualifier, it has exactly one qualifier -- the default qualifier `@Default`."
msgstr "在带注释的参数上声明的限定符会在类型安全的解析过程中被使用。如果接收者未声明任何限定符，则它只有一个限定符——默认限定符 `@Default` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Has qualifiers `[@Default]` and receives signals of type `OrderPlaced` emitted with the `@Default` qualifier. Note that if a `Signal` injection point declares no qualifier, it has exactly one qualifier -- the default qualifier `@Default`."
msgstr "具有 `[@Default]` 限定符，并接收带有 `@Default` 限定符发出的 `OrderPlaced` 类型的信号。请注意，如果某个 `Signal` 注入点未声明限定符，则它恰好有一个限定符——即默认限定符 `@Default` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Has qualifiers `[@Urgent]` and receives signals of type `OrderPlaced` emitted with the `@Urgent` qualifier."
msgstr "具有 `[@Urgent]` 修饰符，并接收带有 `@Urgent` 修饰符发出的 `OrderPlaced` 类型信号。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Has qualifiers `[@Any]` and receives all signals of type `OrderPlaced`."
msgstr "具有 `[@Any]` 限定条件，并接收所有类型为 `OrderPlaced` 的信号。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The fact that a receiver which declares no qualifier has exactly one qualifier -- `@Default` -- is the only difference from the CDI specification, where similar observer methods have an empty set of qualifiers and therefore match any events of a specific type."
msgstr "一个未声明任何限定符的接收器实际上拥有一个限定符 `——@Default——` 这一点 `是` 它与 CDI 规范的唯一区别；而在 CDI 规范中，类似的观察者方法的限定符集为空，因此可匹配任何特定类型的事件。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Return Values"
msgstr "返回值"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A receiver method may return a value, which is used as the response for `request` / `reactive().request()` emissions.\n"
"The return value is ignored for `publish` and `send` emissions.\n"
"The return type is also used during <<receiver-resolution>> -- only receivers whose response type is assignable to the requested type are considered.\n"
"The method can return the value directly, or wrapped in a `Uni` or `CompletionStage`:"
msgstr "接收器方法可能会返回一个值，该值将作为对 `request` / `reactive().request()` 发射的响应。对于 `publish` 和 `send` 发射，返回值将被忽略。返回类型在 <<receiver-resolution>> 过程中也会被使用——只有响应类型可赋值给请求类型的接收器才会被考虑。 该方法可以直接返回该值，也可以将其包装在 `Uni` 或 `CompletionStage` 中："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Signal Context"
msgstr "信号上下文"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The annotated parameter may also be of type `SignalContext<T>` instead of the signal type directly.\n"
"This gives the receiver access to the full signal context, including metadata, qualifiers, and emission type:"
msgstr "注解参数也可以是 `SignalContext<T>` 类型，而不是直接采用信号类型。这样，接收方就可以访问完整的信号上下文，包括元数据、限定符和发射类型："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The execution model determines how a receiver method is invoked.\n"
"It is resolved using the following rules, in order of priority:"
msgstr "执行模型决定了接收器方法的调用方式。其解析遵循以下规则，按优先级顺序进行："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the method is annotated with `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.RunOnVirtualThread`, the execution model is `VIRTUAL_THREAD`."
msgstr "如果该方法标注了 `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.RunOnVirtualThread` 注解，则其执行模型为 `VIRTUAL_THREAD` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the method is annotated with `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.Blocking`, the execution model is `BLOCKING`."
msgstr "如果该方法标注了 `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.Blocking` 注解，则其执行模型为 `BLOCKING` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the method is annotated with `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.NonBlocking`, the execution model is `NON_BLOCKING`."
msgstr "如果该方法标注了 `@io.smallrye.common.annotation.NonBlocking` 注解，则其执行模型为 `NON_BLOCKING` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If none of the above is present on the method, the declaring class is checked for the same annotations."
msgstr "如果该方法上不存在上述任何注解，则会检查声明该方法的类是否带有相同的注解。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If no annotation is found, the default is derived from the method signature:"
msgstr "如果未找到注解，则默认值将根据方法签名推导出来："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A method returning `Uni` or `CompletionStage` defaults to `NON_BLOCKING` -- when Vert.x is available, it is executed on the event loop."
msgstr "返回 `Uni` 或 `CompletionStage` 的方法默认采用 NON_BLOCK `ING 模式——当` Vert.x 可用时，该方法将在事件循环中执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Any other return type defaults to `BLOCKING` -- the method is offloaded to a worker thread."
msgstr "任何其他返回类型默认采用 `BLOCKING — 该` 方法将卸载到一个工作线程上。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Request Context"
msgstr "请求上下文"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Each receiver execution is associated with a new CDI request context.\n"
"This means that `@RequestScoped` beans injected into the receiver method or used by the bean that declares the receiver are unique to that particular invocation."
msgstr "每次接收器的执行都与一个新的 CDI 请求上下文相关联。这意味着注入到接收器方法中，或由声明该接收器的 Bean 所使用的 `@RequestScoped` Bean，仅在该特定调用中有效。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Programmatic Receivers"
msgstr "程序化接收器"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Receivers can also be registered programmatically at runtime via the `Receivers` interface:"
msgstr "还可以通过 `Receivers` 接口在运行时以编程方式注册接收器："

